msgid "If you'd like you can enter a different 'Reply-To' email address. This is the email address that all replies will go to."
msgstr "当然，您也可以输入不同的“回复到”邮件地址。这是收集所有回复邮件的地址。"

#: ../../source/administration.rst:81
msgid "If you do not fill in this value Koha will use the address in the :ref:`ReplytoDefault` preference"
msgstr "如果您不填写此值，Koha 将使用  :ref:`默认回复` 里的地址"

