msgstr ""

#: ../../source/administration.rst:302
msgid "To add a new item type, simply click the 'New item type' button at the top of the Item types page."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/administration.rst:305
msgid "|image135|"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/administration.rst:307
msgid "In the 'Item type' field, enter a short code for your item type (maximum of 10 characters)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/administration.rst:310
msgid "The the 'Parent item type' field, you can choose an item type that will act as a parent category for this item type. You can then define :ref:`circulation rules <circulation-and-fines-rules-label>` based on those parent item types."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/administration.rst:315
msgid "For example, you could have DVD and Blu-ray item types, and the DVD would be the parent of the Blu-ray item type."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/administration.rst:318
msgid "|image1510|"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/administration.rst:320
msgid "You can then create a :ref:`circulation rule <circulation-and-fines-rules-label>` for either Blu-ray only or DVD and Blu-ray (DVD (All))"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/administration.rst:323
msgid "|image1511|"
msgstr ""

