msgstr ""

#: ../../source/administration.rst:330
msgid "Item types can be grouped together for searching at the same time. For example you can put DVDs and Blu-rays in to a group called Movie and then they can be searched together. These groups are defined in the ITEMTYPECAT :ref:`authorized value category <existing-values-label>`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/administration.rst:335
msgid "You can choose to have an image associated with your item type"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/administration.rst:337
msgid "You can choose from a series of image collections"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/administration.rst:339
msgid "You can link to a remote image"
msgstr ""

