msgstr ""

#: ../../source/administration.rst:361
msgid "If you want to completely hide items from a certain item type, let's say that you have a professional library with books reserved for staff and you don't want those to appear in the OPAC, use the :ref:`OpacHiddenItems` system preference."
msgstr ""

